Name: Official Dossier from the Hollow Investigative Association
Desc2:
From what content remains, it seems to read:
"Hollow Investigative Association Decision on Citizens Trespassing Through Hollow Zero" 
"Please take the two girls back to school, and re-educate them on Hollow safety procedures.
Hollow Zero is the highest-risk area in New Eridu. Please do not enter of your own accord."
